{"word":"G5398 - φοβερός - phoberós - fob-er-os' - Fearful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φοβερός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phoberós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fob-er-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fearful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பயங்கரமாயிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. inspiring fear, terrible, formidable"},{"paragraph":"2. affected with fear, timid"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>; <i>frightful</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>formidable:</i> - fearful, terrible.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}